Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.37,0:00:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫江戶川柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.89,0:00:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本是個高中生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.21,0:00:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不倖被歹徒灌下毒藥而變小了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.91,0:00:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過雖然變小了 頭腦還是一樣的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.59,0:00:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個不摺不扣的名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.85,0:00:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的事件發生在高樓裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.55,0:00:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手利用電梯作案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.11,0:00:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而即使隱藏在兩扇門之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.71,0:00:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相只有一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.82,0:01:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電梯殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.48,0:02:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.45,0:02:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就是假日 怎麽會塞車塞成這個樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.55,0:02:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果搭電車會不會比較快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.27,0:02:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像做夢一樣沒有想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.74,0:02:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以當戶屋小姐的服裝模特兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.65,0:02:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方真的是叫戶屋英子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.08,0:02:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那位被稱作爲...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.97,0:02:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本首屈一指的頂尖設計師戶屋英子 對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.03,0:02:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.94,0:02:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位戶屋英子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.64,0:03:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早陣子舉辦的時裝表演好像突然暫停的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.50,0:03:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是他們的競爭對手早一步舉行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.42,0:03:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個跟他們差不多款式的冬季時裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.82,0:03:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才被迫暫停的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.47,0:03:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很清楚 叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.11,0:03:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會是戶屋英子迷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.97,0:03:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.37,0:03:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.77,0:03:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵探是必須常常關心社會以便擴展自己的商業觸角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.64,0:03:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這會有什麽觸角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.79,0:03:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.21,0:03:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的建築物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.22,0:03:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔你又不是來這裏當模特兒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.17,0:03:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個小鬼一直唠唠叨叨的 很吵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.26,0:03:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我叫做毛利蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.57,0:03:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先確認一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.22,0:03:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長馬上就回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.23,0:03:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您在那邊稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.82,0:04:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.86,0:04:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏相當的安靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.95,0:04:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 因爲今天是假日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.62,0:04:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒有其他的人在 很安靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.35,0:04:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉毛利小姐 等很久了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.73,0:04:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.93,0:04:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.77,0:04:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.76,0:04:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是不是在流行那種大皮包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.42,0:04:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲她是那種走在流行尖端的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.15,0:04:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後一定會開始流行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.66,0:04:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.96,0:04:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是我爸爸 還有江戶川柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.71,0:04:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們硬要跟我來 所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.81,0:04:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是毛利小五郎 我女兒這次就蔴煩您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.40,0:04:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.84,0:04:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個名偵探啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.17,0:04:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏 你聽過敝人的名字 真是無限的榮倖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.17,0:04:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的一點小小心意 請笑納
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.77,0:04:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戶屋老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.37,0:04:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.57,0:04:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.40,0:05:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.97,0:05:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.21,0:05:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我的秘書谷口美香小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.04,0:05:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是谷口美香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.53,0:05:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是毛利蘭小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.31,0:05:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟她的父親小五郎先生 還有這位...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.90,0:05:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是江戶川柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.16,0:05:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.21,0:05:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思 禮拜天休息還蔴煩你到這兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.63,0:05:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.70,0:05:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來就是想請老師讓我辭職
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.74,0:05:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因爲戶屋老師你連假日都還要強迫我來上班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.67,0:05:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 隨你高興吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.67,0:05:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去一趟社長室 把收到的花整理一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.23,0:05:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且拿一些文件過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.18,0:05:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請你們在那邊的座位稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.10,0:05:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也請柯南小朋友跟令尊一起過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.46,0:05:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.32,0:05:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美香小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.51,0:05:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽蔴煩你先到八樓的服裝配件室先準備一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.50,0:05:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 待會兒見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.14,0:05:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.02,0:06:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那位秘書是不是要嚮公司辭職
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.04,0:06:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.08,0:06:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說她好像已經提出了辭職了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.36,0:06:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此的感情好像不太好 爲什麽還幫她按按鈕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.64,0:06:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我們就在這兒等吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.37,0:06:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我要去廁所一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.51,0:06:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.95,0:06:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你們快去快回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.91,0:06:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.19,0:06:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個有沒有洗手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.63,0:06:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江田先生 蔴煩你一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.90,0:06:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.89,0:06:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從社長室打美香小姐的行動電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.78,0:06:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是都沒有人接
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.73,0:06:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能請你跟我過去看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.55,0:06:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.62,0:06:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛那麽緊張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.95,0:06:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過手機沒人接而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.61,0:06:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.07,0:07:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷口小姐所搭乘的電梯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.06,0:07:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直停在八樓都沒有動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.49,0:07:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麽事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.34,0:07:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.27,0:07:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們先搭這邊的電梯到上面去看看到底怎麽回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.81,0:07:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麽事情了 英子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.24,0:07:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是秘書谷口美香小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.66,0:07:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 地闆上有鞋印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.06,0:07:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞋印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.30,0:07:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.41,0:07:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依我看恐怕是安全梯裏面的灰塵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.24,0:07:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是強盜想闖空門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.21,0:07:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壞人跑進來發現美香小姐 就把她給刺死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.99,0:07:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看她的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.48,0:08:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像早就知道會發生這種事情一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.80,0:08:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江田先生 能不能請你從裏面把門卡住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.24,0:08:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.27,0:08:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.16,0:08:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些鞋印...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.16,0:08:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一刀直達心髒幾乎是當場死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.07,0:08:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.11,0:08:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個鞋印有二十六公分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.07,0:08:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有二十六公分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.92,0:08:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽嫌疑犯是個男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.95,0:08:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩膀的地方有血蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.92,0:08:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且衣服的肩膀部分還有這種明顯的摺痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.95,0:09:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個比平常人更註重穿著的服裝界人士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.29,0:09:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會穿這種有摺痕的衣服出門嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.43,0:09:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最不可思議的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.10,0:09:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她倒在地上的方嚮竟然是嚮著電梯外面仰躺著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.03,0:09:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她是走出電梯被兇手一刀擊斃的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.34,0:09:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是倒在電梯裏面才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.36,0:09:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此有可能是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.60,0:09:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手把倒在電梯裏面的谷口小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.54,0:09:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意改變方嚮把她移動到走廊的那一方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.03,0:09:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.15,0:09:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麽要這樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.91,0:09:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和谷口小姐是分別搭乘兩部電梯上樓的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.03,0:09:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我所搭乘的就是那邊那部電梯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.73,0:09:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十五樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.64,0:09:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是直達十五樓的都沒有停的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.41,0:09:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 都沒有停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.79,0:09:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽谷口美香小姐所搭乘的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.95,0:09:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是正中間這部電梯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.04,0:09:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那部電梯是直達八樓以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.21,0:10:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從九樓到十五樓每一層都會停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.64,0:10:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽我們現在所搭乘的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.10,0:10:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是到八樓的各樓層都會停的電梯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.96,0:10:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.29,0:10:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到十五樓的電梯只有兩部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.83,0:10:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽戶屋小姐搭上電梯之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.37,0:10:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再回到這裏來大概需要花多少時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.60,0:10:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩分鍾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.85,0:10:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不..我想也有可能一分多鍾吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.95,0:10:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不到兩分鍾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.62,0:10:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.63,0:10:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏的鞋印一直連接到樓梯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.08,0:10:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而一樓通往外面的緊急出口並沒有上鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.68,0:10:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最後巡視是什麽時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.53,0:10:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生命案的兩小時之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.60,0:10:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個時候確實是上鎖的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.44,0:10:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後又有誰出入這棟大樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.96,0:10:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了社長之外就沒有其他人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.10,0:10:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.05,0:10:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲我有資料需要調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.07,0:10:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此大概在一個小時以前進公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.87,0:10:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在社長室待了約三十分鍾以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.17,0:10:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就到外面喝咖啡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.33,0:11:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是從大門出去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.24,0:11:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官 這一切正像英子小姐所說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.45,0:11:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是強盜闖空門的時候所犯下的案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.82,0:11:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手從外面把一樓的緊急出口的鎖撬開之後潛入大樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.44,0:11:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再爬樓梯到八樓去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.94,0:11:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他經過八樓電梯前面的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.41,0:11:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛好遇見谷口小姐出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.33,0:11:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手立刻刺殺了谷口小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.62,0:11:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再利用樓梯逃到外面去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.76,0:11:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 立刻調查這附近一帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.50,0:11:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有戶屋小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.85,0:11:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要採集你的指紋 請你合作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.01,0:11:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官先生 你的意思是我也是兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.14,0:11:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我們是爲了要找出兇手的指紋 所以說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.41,0:11:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上你不可能會有嫌疑的 放心好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.97,0:11:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麽她不可能是殺人兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.87,0:11:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個笨蛋 你知不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.32,0:11:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英子小姐跟谷口小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.41,0:11:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是同時搭乘兩部不同的電梯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.17,0:12:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且谷口小姐是在到達八樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.57,0:12:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門一打開之後就被刺殺身亡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.24,0:12:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候英子小姐是在十五樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.61,0:12:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那裏並沒有到達八樓的電梯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.10,0:12:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她如何能夠殺死谷口小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.12,0:12:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是也是不能完全排除嫌疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.49,0:12:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼 這種專業的工作你不要插嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.28,0:12:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你也不需要打人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.42,0:12:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲我每次用說的都沒有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.12,0:12:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔真差勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.64,0:12:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法靠他了 好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.13,0:12:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你要去哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.76,0:12:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.37,0:12:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說我的推理是正確的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.26,0:12:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽事情的關鍵應該在十五樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.59,0:12:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是社長室專屬的樓層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.72,0:12:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的地毯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.01,0:12:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花瓣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.06,0:13:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花粉嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.71,0:13:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.52,0:13:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粘過膠帶的痕蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.76,0:13:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樣的花粉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.84,0:13:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是爲什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.52,0:13:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麽這裏會有花瓣跟花粉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.87,0:13:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果去社長室 應該不會掉在這裏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.25,0:13:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷口小姐是電梯停在八樓的時候被刺殺身亡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.08,0:13:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戶屋英子空白的時間只有短短的一分多鍾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.41,0:13:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從第十五樓爬樓梯下到第八樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.42,0:13:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她殺了之後再回到十五樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.70,0:14:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最少也要花個四到五分鍾左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.14,0:14:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.44,0:14:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題就在殺她的地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.20,0:14:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷口小姐屍體所倒下的方嚮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.98,0:14:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩膀上的血蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.65,0:14:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不自然的衣服摺痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.77,0:14:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉落在地上的花瓣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.21,0:14:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.32,0:14:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殘留在另外一臺電梯按鈕上的膠帶痕蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.11,0:14:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.00,0:14:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她想利用電梯設下不在場的證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.40,0:14:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺死谷口小姐的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.28,0:14:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然就是戶屋英子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.01,0:14:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有兇手的指紋嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.48,0:14:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 刀子還有一樓的緊急出口的門上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.28,0:14:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒有辦法檢驗出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.43,0:14:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 警官先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.65,0:14:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是可以回傢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.63,0:14:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.82,0:14:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就這樣吧..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.76,0:14:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蹧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.65,0:14:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣的話 證據會被戶屋英子處理掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.29,0:15:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.39,0:15:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好再蔴煩叔叔來做推理了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.06,0:15:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.19,0:15:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.03,0:15:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我們改天好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.12,0:15:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.43,0:15:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽 我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.43,0:15:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你到門口好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.32,0:15:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.88,0:15:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 你還不能回去 抱歉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.75,0:15:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.97,0:15:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺害谷口美香小姐的兇手 就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.13,0:15:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.19,0:15:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說些什麽 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.21,0:15:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得你不是剛剛才說過她不可能是兇手的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.32,0:15:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的確是說過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.89,0:15:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個只是個圈套而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.15,0:15:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圈套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.01,0:15:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先說明關於八樓走廊上所留下來的鞋印吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.41,0:15:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔴煩你先坐下來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.81,0:16:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是她爲了要讓谷口美香之死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.85,0:16:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來像是強盜闖空門所犯下的案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.38,0:16:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事先做好的陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.28,0:16:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你們回想一下那些鞋印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.17,0:16:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通常殺了人之後應該是跑著逃走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.68,0:16:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麽一來步伐應該很大才對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.64,0:16:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那些鞋印好像是故意來回走動的步伐 對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.32,0:16:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 聽你這麽說的確是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.37,0:16:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.62,0:16:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在事件發生前的一個小時來到大樓僞造了鞋印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.61,0:16:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再從一樓的緊急出口內側事先把門鎖給打開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.19,0:16:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.33,0:16:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又把不合腳的運動鞋藏在你的大皮包裏走出大樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.61,0:16:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三十分鍾以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.02,0:16:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把運動鞋處理掉 再回到這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.37,0:16:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後你看到我們在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.07,0:16:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和谷口美香小姐一起往電梯的方嚮走去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.26,0:17:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候按電梯按鈕的人是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.50,0:17:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.73,0:17:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何你都有必要讓谷口小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.62,0:17:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭上那部最靠近你那邊的中央電梯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.30,0:17:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.44,0:17:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你開始在電梯裏面打行動電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.56,0:17:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到了十五樓之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.01,0:17:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再按下最後的按鍵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.32,0:17:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲在電梯裏面行動電話是相當不容易接通的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.95,0:17:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在電話裏面對谷口小姐說 請他立刻到十五樓來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.52,0:17:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.92,0:17:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把硬幣用膠帶貼在十五樓的電梯按鈕上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.97,0:17:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是爲了在殺美香小姐的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.84,0:17:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓電梯的門關起來的緣故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.14,0:17:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你等一下 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.00,0:17:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被害者是在八樓被殺死的 這怎麽解釋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.66,0:18:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始就是圈套的重點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.64,0:18:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷口小姐倒在地上的方嚮 難道你不覺的很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.45,0:18:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果谷口小姐是在走出電梯的時候被兇手刺殺的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.50,0:18:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是倒在電梯裏面才對的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.11,0:18:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她卻是朝嚮電梯的外面倒下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.22,0:18:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 照你這麽說的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.49,0:18:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英子小姐是在十五樓刺殺谷口小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.57,0:18:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再趕緊跑到她的後方將谷口小姐抱住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.69,0:18:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把方嚮改成朝著走廊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.06,0:18:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後按下到八樓的按鈕 再把貼在按鈕的膠帶撕下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.21,0:18:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後你就撐著谷口小姐的背部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.20,0:18:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他保持坐著的狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.99,0:18:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己再跑到外面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.80,0:18:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓電梯把她送到八樓去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.11,0:18:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽..戶屋小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.38,0:18:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要解開不在場證明的圈套 有兩個關鍵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.45,0:19:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個就是留在谷口小姐肩膀上的摺痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.77,0:19:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你在假造證據的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.29,0:19:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服被電梯的門夾住所留下來的痕蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.11,0:19:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.30,0:19:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你爲了要殺谷口小姐把礙事的花放在地闆上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.36,0:19:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以十五樓的地毯上面才會留下花瓣和花粉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.54,0:19:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的故事真有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.75,0:19:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你的假設未免太有想象力了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.15,0:19:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.41,0:19:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷口小姐如果從八樓再一次搭乘電梯的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.07,0:19:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那八樓的按鈕上應該會有她的指紋才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.30,0:19:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果怎麽樣 警官先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.08,0:19:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按鈕上面有指紋嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.04,0:19:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 上面並沒有任何人的指紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.78,0:19:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾的 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.52,0:19:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美香小姐根本就沒有去過十五樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.11,0:19:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的假設完全被推翻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.32,0:19:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 因爲那是被你擦掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.82,0:19:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確實是很厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.88,0:19:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲了要讓電梯的門停止運動 你就按了電梯的按鈕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.48,0:19:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用手指把指紋給擦掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.78,0:20:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂..有沒有證據可以證明這點啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.75,0:20:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然有證據了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.69,0:20:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在英子小姐的皮包裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.41,0:20:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有什麽樣的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.20,0:20:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在犯案的時候所使用的沾有血蹟的手套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.37,0:20:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理論上應該是沒有時間可以把手套處理掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.51,0:20:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何況也不能將牠藏在公司裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.80,0:20:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.15,0:20:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對電梯的不在場證明這個計劃相當的有把握
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.11,0:20:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我認爲沾了血蹟的手套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.49,0:20:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了在你身上之外 不可能放在其牠的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.81,0:20:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 那是因爲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.08,0:20:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷口小姐就是偷走你的服裝設計賣給競爭公司的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.74,0:20:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.91,0:20:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,證據確實在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.63,0:20:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這一切都是谷口她背叛我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.28,0:20:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說即使我告到警察局也沒有關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.13,0:20:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲服裝表演還是會被迫暫停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.43,0:20:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這樣只會讓戶屋英子這個品牌受到更大的傷害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.55,0:21:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後她立刻嚮公司提出了辭呈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.22,0:21:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何我都要趁她還在公司的時候 把她給殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.83,0:21:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會發生今天這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.21,0:21:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我聽到跟你一起來的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.79,0:21:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那位鼎鼎大名的名偵探毛利小五郎的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.40,0:21:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一時之間驚慌失措
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.71,0:21:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是機會只剩下今天而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.31,0:23:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.54,0:23:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許你不相信我所說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.99,0:23:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我真的是想請你當我們公司的模特兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.61,0:23:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很希望戶屋英子的服裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.76,0:23:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能有像你這樣身心都很健康的人來穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.99,0:23:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很可惜 小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.28,0:23:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才有機會可以當模特兒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.10,0:23:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.98,0:23:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了 爸爸他人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.63,0:23:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蹧糕 叔叔還睡在那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.56,0:23:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的樣子好像一直在忍耐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.70,0:23:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲他是戶屋英子迷卻又得拆穿她的罪行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.20,0:23:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果叔叔知道拆穿她罪行的人是我的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.81,0:23:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會被扁的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.21,0:24:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.49,0:24:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 幽靈的真面目是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.70,0:24:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.08,0:24:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼屋殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:30.52,0:24:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.95,0:24:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛骨悚然的地下室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.67,0:24:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集是個有點恐怖的故事哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.76,0:00:21.19,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相隔百年的世紀末
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.85,0:00:27.40,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在應該流淚的時候我卻笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.03,0:00:39.51,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相隔太久太久的世紀末
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.20,0:00:45.62,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我飛奔嚮廣闊無邊的新世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.13,0:00:52.15,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些在我孩童時代還一知半解的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.30,0:00:58.59,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在長大以後還是這樣不太明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.89,0:01:01.59,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麽了不起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.85,0:01:04.60,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更算不上是出色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.85,0:01:11.02,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所知道的只有 心裏忐忑不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.15,0:01:16.90,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那並不是答案 也並非是真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.17,0:01:22.95,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所相信的是 只有心的悸動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.21,0:01:28.45,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心裏的忐忑和不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.05,0:21:44.40,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是我的想象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.60,0:21:49.02,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喝著涼了一半的紅茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.29,0:21:54.16,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩弄著纏繞在手指上的細繩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.94,0:22:03.16,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴著BOSSA NOVO的節奏腳歩變得輕快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.36,0:22:08.17,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謎底就在我手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.46,0:22:14.47,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 Ah- Ah- Ah-
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.65,0:22:24.31,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同的裝束 相同的地點 下週我也會在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.70,0:22:26.82,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一步接一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.00,0:22:31.74,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不必對他心生厭倦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.71,0:22:33.86,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個案件接一個案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.07,0:22:38.16,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎爾是否笑話我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.61,0:22:43.25,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在無盡的日子以外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.43,0:22:47.87,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有他在等待著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.35,0:22:52.42,LRC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要走我自己的路
